  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/752053a23dec376a7397bcf244c94054.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual fish-raising simulation game \"Idle Aquarium\" is conveniently displayed on your screen, allowing you to enjoy the joy of being a fish keeper while working.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed Your Fish:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your little fish, make friends with them, unlock new species, and even some very rare ones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/57cc8fc5e09b6af7d7ee36874ece03ad.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/57cc8fc5e09b6af7d7ee36874ece03ad.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/57cc8fc5e09b6af7d7ee36874ece03ad.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decorate Your Aquarium:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your aquarium and turn your desktop into your favorite style, with a variety of decorations to meet all your needs. Whether it's a planted tank or a South American tank, any style you want is possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multitasking Capability:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comfortably placed at the bottom of the screen, you can take care of your fish while accomplishing other tasks. Or switch to \"Focus Mode\" to quietly enjoy them without much interaction.A casual fish-raising simulation game \"Idle Aquarium\" is conveniently displayed on your screen, allowing you to enjoy the fun of being a fish keeper while working.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your little fish, make friends with them, unlock new species, decorate your aquarium, and turn your desktop into your favorite style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect your Steam Drops:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you play, you will have a chance to drop a steam item, There is a surprise for you to collect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/bd9c85b57ffdc1e21fae3ad899c7044d.avif?t=1741755164\" width=792 height=286 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/752053a23dec376a7397bcf244c94054.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual fish-raising simulation game \"Idle Aquarium\" is conveniently displayed on your screen, allowing you to enjoy the joy of being a fish keeper while working.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed Your Fish:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your little fish, make friends with them, unlock new species, and even some very rare ones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/57cc8fc5e09b6af7d7ee36874ece03ad.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/57cc8fc5e09b6af7d7ee36874ece03ad.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/57cc8fc5e09b6af7d7ee36874ece03ad.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decorate Your Aquarium:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your aquarium and turn your desktop into your favorite style, with a variety of decorations to meet all your needs. Whether it's a planted tank or a South American tank, any style you want is possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multitasking Capability:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comfortably placed at the bottom of the screen, you can take care of your fish while accomplishing other tasks. Or switch to \"Focus Mode\" to quietly enjoy them without much interaction.A casual fish-raising simulation game \"Idle Aquarium\" is conveniently displayed on your screen, allowing you to enjoy the fun of being a fish keeper while working.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your little fish, make friends with them, unlock new species, decorate your aquarium, and turn your desktop into your favorite style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect your Steam Drops:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you play, you will have a chance to drop a steam item, There is a surprise for you to collect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/bd9c85b57ffdc1e21fae3ad899c7044d.avif?t=1741755164\" width=792 height=286 /></span></p>",
